                <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#A3C4AA;line-height:1.5;margin:0;">DevSecOps market expanding from <strong style="color:#E2FFE8;">$9–11.7B USD</strong> in 2025–26 toward <strong style="color:#E2FFE8;">$16–37B by 2030–35</strong>, driven by cloud-native workloads and regulatory pressure.</p>
