                <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#A3C4AA;line-height:1.5;margin:0;">Cloud-based DevSecOps accounts for <strong style="color:#E2FFE8;">~61%</strong> of deployments; cloud-native environments hold <strong style="color:#E2FFE8;">~48% share</strong>. Kubernetes and containers are now the primary security context.</p>
