                <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#A3C4AA;line-height:1.5;margin:0;">SAST, SCA, secrets detection, and IaC scanning embedded in CI/CD at <strong style="color:#E2FFE8;">commit and PR time</strong>. Security gates replacing post-release audits.</p>
