                <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#A3C4AA;line-height:1.5;margin:0;"><strong style="color:#E2FFE8;">SBOMs, dependency signing, and OSS risk</strong> are the fastest-growing segments following high-profile pipeline compromises (SolarWinds, XZ Utils, etc.).</p>
