                <div>
                    <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.78rem;color:#FFA500;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:0.2rem;">Alert Fatigue &amp; Poor Prioritization</div>
                    <p style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#A3C4AA;margin:0;line-height:1.5;">Teams cannot separate exploitable, critical issues from noise — leading to missed vulnerabilities or blocked pipelines slowing release velocity.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="orange-card reveal" style="padding:0.85rem 1.2rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:1rem;">
